                                <condition>The ogham inscription is considerably worn by weather and cattle scratching. Macalister (Pilsworth and Macalister 1940, 92) speculates that <q>the second angle has been wilfully mutilated</q>. A piece of the inscribed angle has been broken off and the beginning of the final name has been lost.</condition>
